name: "Cube of Weirdness (In Motion)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing and collage created and animated with a free app on my laptop.] Consider this piece a warning. The world is still spinning, but shit's getting weird. If we don't do something to combat all of this cultural insecurity, we'll inevitably find ourselves being flung off the surface of the planet into the cold void of space. And then where will we buy our donuts? ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
